description: The ultimate combination of city and coastal living collide at these newer construction waterfront homes ideally located in South Boston's City Point with ocean views and top-of-the-line finishes! This thoughtfully designed residence is our last remaining Penthouse, offering approximately 1,341 SQFT of open living space, two bedrooms, two bathrooms, a custom two toned kitchen with paneled appliances, beverage center, sleek quartz countertops with a waterfall edge, floor-to-ceiling windows, open concept living and dining, gas fireplace, huge primary suite featuring large custom built-out closets, beautifully tiled spa-like primary bathroom & a curbless glass enclosed steam shower. This home features smart home technology throughout and complete w/ private outdoor space, large deeded storage, one garage parking space, common area with gas grills and gas fire pit and a prime location offering convenient access to beaches, yacht clubs, parks and all the neighborhood has to offer!
